title: All-marshmallow Lucky Charms available through online contest
text:
(CNN) - Get out your lucky charms because an all-marshmallow version of Lucky Charms will be awarded to 10 winners of an online contest.
General Mills said it will produce 10 boxes of the "unicorn of the cereal world." Those interested in taking home the sweet concoction must post a photo of themselves to Facebook, Twitter or Instagram with an "imaginary" box of Lucky Charms.
The hashtag " #Lucky10Sweepstakes " is also compulsory.
The contest runs through Oct. 18.
